        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Quick Verdict</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-400">
          Square Appointments is a solid choice for solo artists who need simple scheduling tied to Square Payments. The free starter plan is genuinely useful â€?for a single artist with basic needs.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-400">
          For any studio with multiple artists, the picture changes. <strong class="text-accent-300">InkFlow</strong> replaces Square Appointments, Square for Retail, a separate waiver app, and an email marketing tool â€?four products replaced by one. Including features Square doesn't offer at any price: deposit-based booking that actually collects payment, artist commission splitting, and tattoo aftercare automation.
