        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 p-5">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Payroll & team management</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">Square offers integrated payroll and team management tools. InkFlow focuses on studio operations â€?payroll integration is on the roadmap but not yet available.</p>
