        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-4"><span class="flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent-500/20 text-accent-400 font-bold text-sm">3</span>
          <div><strong class="text-white">Import clients</strong><p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">Use InkFlow CSV import to upload your client database. Set up your service menu and deposit amounts.</p></div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-4"><span class="flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent-500/20 text-accent-400 font-bold text-sm">4</span>
          <div><strong class="text-white">Connect Stripe and go live</strong><p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">Connect your Stripe account (or create one). Your booking page is live immediately. Keep Square running for existing appointments during a 1-2 week transition.</p></div>
        </li>
      </ol>
      <div class="mt-6 rounded-lg bg-ink-900/50 border border-ink-800 p-4">
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">đź“ž <strong class="text-white">Need help?</strong> We offer free migration assistance. Email hello@ink-flows.com.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-16 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Replace 4 Square Products With One Platform</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-gray-400 max-w-xl mx-auto">Free to start. No hardware. No contracts. Built for tattoo studios.</p>
    <a href="https://app.ink-flows.com/register" class="mt-6 inline-block rounded-lg bg-accent-500 px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-ink-950 hover:bg-accent-400 transition-all">Try InkFlow Free â†?/a>
    <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-600"><a href="/pricing" class="text-accent-400 hover:underline">Compare plans</a></p>
  </section>

  <!-- Methodology -->
  <section class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-8">
